        "穗氏家族。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "穗"
    }
  ],
  "formations": [
    {
      "formation_type": "phono_semantic_compound",
      "original_sense_index": 0,
      "note": "形声字，从禾，惠声，禾表示植物，惠表示读音，最初指谷物的穗。"
    }
